Examine the various control structures in php and construct a bank transaction problem
with customers deposit and withdrawal of amount.
<?php
$balance = 5000;
$transactionType = "withdraw";
$amount = 2000;
if ($transactionType == "deposit") {
$balance += $amount;
echo "Deposit successful! New balance is Rs. $balance.";
} elseif ($transactionType == "withdraw") {
if ($amount <= $balance) {
$balance -= $amount;
echo "Withdrawal successful! New balance is Rs. $balance.";
} else {
echo "Insufficient balance! Withdrawal failed.";
}
} else {
echo "Invalid transaction type!";
}
?>
OUTPUT:
Withdrawal successful! New balance is Rs. 3000.
